claim.claim-text:
A sleep sensor (10) which is attached to a user who is sleeping when it is to be used, characterized by comprising:
a first detector (111) configured to detect an acceleration signal representing acceleration that is obtained from the sleep sensor;
an estimation module (112) configured to estimate the user's body position based on the detected acceleration signal;
a second detector (113) configured to detect a signal for estimating a state other than the user's body position; and
a control module (115) configured to operate the second detector when the estimated user's body position is at least one of predefined body positions.
